description:
NetBeans is an integrated development environment for programming in Java and many other languages.

This package corresponds to the HTML5 and Javascript bundle (it include PHP bundle too).

This is a meta package to match the two bundles (PHP and HTML / JS) existing on the official website but which are identical.

![screenshot](https://cdn.rawgit.com/Akipe/chocolatey-packages/92815e35/icons/netbeans/netbeans-screenshot.png)
summary: An open source IDE that support different language and technologies.
author: Oracle Corporation
